UK #Vaccine update. Thank you 💙NHS!

As of data up to 13 Feb 2021:

537,715 people (1.02% of UK adults) have completed their full, recommended, course of 𝗧𝗪𝗢 vaccinations against #Covid19.

15,062,189 people (28.60% of UK adults) have had one #vaccination.
